---
import LayoutAuthority from '@/layouts/LayoutAuthority.astro';
---

<LayoutAuthority title="Privacy Policy | Marketing by Bešić">
  <section class="min-h-screen py-20 md:py-32">
    <div class="container-custom max-w-3xl">
      <h1 class="heading-xl mb-12">Privacy Policy</h1>

      <div class="prose prose-lg prose-invert max-w-none space-y-8">
        <p class="body-md">
          <strong>Last updated:</strong> April 2026
        </p>

        <section>
          <h2 class="heading-md mb-4">1. Data Controller</h2>
          <p class="body-md">
            BEŠIĆ j.d.o.o. za usluge, Zagreb, Croatia, managed by Dino Bešić, is the data controller for all personal data collected through this website.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="heading-md mb-4">2. Data We Collect</h2>
          <p class="body-md">
            We collect the following personal data:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside body-md space-y-1">
            <li>Email address (via newsletter subscription)</li>
            <li>First name (optional, via newsletter subscription)</li>
            <li>Usage data via Google Tag Manager and Meta Pixel (with your consent)</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="heading-md mb-4">3. Legal Basis (GDPR)</h2>
          <p class="body-md">
            We process your data based on your explicit consent (GDPR Article 6(1)(a)). You may withdraw consent at any time by contacting us at info@marketingbybesic.com.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="heading-md mb-4">4. Third-Party Services</h2>
          <p class="body-md">
            We use the following third-party services that may process your data:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside body-md space-y-1">
            <li><strong>SendFox:</strong> Newsletter subscription management</li>
            <li><strong>Google Tag Manager (GTM-5GL56SKX):</strong> Analytics and tracking</li>
            <li><strong>Meta Pixel (1978765049417651):</strong> Advertising analytics</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="body-md mt-4">
            These services are only activated after you provide explicit cookie consent via our GDPR banner.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="heading-md mb-4">5. Your Rights</h2>
          <p class="body-md">
            Under GDPR, you have the right to:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside body-md space-y-1">
            <li>Access your personal data</li>
            <li>Rectify inaccurate data</li>
            <li>Request erasure ("right to be forgotten")</li>
            <li>Restrict or object to processing</li>
            <li>Data portability</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="body-md mt-4">
            To exercise any of these rights, email us at <a href="mailto:info@marketingbybesic.com" class="text-brand hover:underline">info@marketingbybesic.com</a>.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="heading-md mb-4">6. Data Retention</h2>
          <p class="body-md">
            We retain your data only as long as necessary for the purposes outlined in this policy, or as required by law. Newsletter data is retained until you unsubscribe.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="heading-md mb-4">7. Contact</h2>
          <p class="body-md">
            For any privacy-related inquiries, contact us at <a href="mailto:info@marketingbybesic.com" class="text-brand hover:underline">info@marketingbybesic.com</a>.
          </p>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</LayoutAuthority>
